<div class='separator'>
<b>How does it work?</b>
<ol>
<li>Log in with Facebook.</li>
<li>Choose friends in your network whom you'd like to be 'friends with benefits' with.</li>
<li>If a friend chooses you back, you get notified.</li>
<li>Use a Key to reveal their identity and take the relationship to the next level.</li>
</ol>
</div>

<div class='separator'>
<b>Will my friends know that I've chosen them as my "Friends with Benefits"?</b>
<p>No, your friends will not know that you chose them.  You identity will only be revealed to your friends when they also choose you as their "Friend with Benefits".</p>
</div>

<div class='separator'>
<b>What are Keys?</b>
<p>Whenever we find a match for you (i.e. you and your friend both choose each other as a Friend with Benefits), your friend is placed in the 'Your Friends with Benefits' box.</p>
<p>To reveal them, simply purchase Keys to unlock their identities.</p>
</div>

<div class='separator'>
<b>Why do you need to collect my email address?</b>
<p>We need your email address to send you email notifications only. We will never spam or share your email address. </p>
</div>

