<b>What are anonymous invites?</b>
<p>The more of your friends use friends-with-benefits.me, the higher the chance you get picked.</p>
<p>An anonymous invite allows you to send an email invitation to your friends to join friends-with-benefits.me without exposing your identity, so they will never know who invited them.</p>
